title: The Uncertain Future of Guardians of the Galaxy
description:
This video is sponsored by Brilliant. Go to https://brilliant.org/Midnight/ and sign up for free 30 day trial, the first 200 people that go to that link will get 20% off the annual Premium subscription.
With GotG Vol. 3 finally out, the future for the series looks more uncertain than ever. In this video I go over if Marvel should continue the adventures of the Guardians and Star Lord in the MCU at all.
